                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a ghost is destroyed, it re-forms after [[/br 2d4 #days]]{2d4 days} within the location it's bound to, fully healed. A ghost can be permanently destroyed only if someone determines the reason for its existence and sets right whatever prevents the spirit from resting.</p>"
